<paragraph blockId="1.[136,1451,496,630]" pageId="1" pageNumber="206">
Notes:— 
<taxonomicName authority="var. oreophilum" authorityName="Koch var. oreophilum" authorityYear="1849" box="[237,681,496,523]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Scrophulariaceae" genus="Verbascum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="1" pageNumber="206" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="oreophilum" variety="oreophilum">
<emphasis box="[237,496,496,522]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="206">Verbascum oreophilum</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis box="[553,681,496,522]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="206">oreophilum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has not been recorded previously from 
<collectingCountry box="[1132,1181,497,523]" name="Iran" pageId="1" pageNumber="206">Iran</collectingCountry>
. However, it is reported from the northwest in 
<collectingCountry box="[380,503,532,558]" name="Azerbaijan" pageId="1" pageNumber="206">Azerbaijan</collectingCountry>
(
<figureCitation box="[517,581,532,558]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="1.[136,245,1563,1589]" captionTargetBox="[346,1241,688,1534]" captionTargetId="figure-117@1.[340,1247,688,1539]" captionTargetPageId="1" captionText="FIGURE 1. Distribution map of V. oreophilum var. joannis (■), V. oreophilum var. oreophilum () V. cheiranthifolium var. transcaspicum (),V. cheiranthifolium var. asperulum ()." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5145473" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5145473/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="206">Fig. 1</figureCitation>
). 
<taxonomicName authority="var. oreophilum" authorityName="Koch var. oreophilum" authorityYear="1849" box="[605,1043,532,559]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Scrophulariaceae" genus="Verbascum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="1" pageNumber="206" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="oreophilum" variety="oreophilum">
<emphasis box="[605,862,532,558]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="206">Verbascum oreophilum</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis box="[915,1043,532,558]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="206">oreophilum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
differs from 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Huber-Morath" authorityYear="1971" baseAuthorityName="Bordz." box="[1188,1317,533,559]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Scrophulariaceae" genus="Verbascum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="1" pageNumber="206" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="oreophilum" variety="joannis">
var. 
<emphasis box="[1235,1317,533,558]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="206">joannis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
on filament hair color. The former 
<taxonomicName box="[396,520,568,594]" pageId="1" pageNumber="206" rank="variety" variety="has">variety has</taxonomicName>
filaments with purple-violet hairs while the later 
<taxonomicName box="[1089,1212,568,594]" pageId="1" pageNumber="206" rank="variety" variety="has">variety has</taxonomicName>
whitish yellow hairs (
<figureCitation box="[144,223,604,630]" captionStart="FIGURE 2" captionStartId="2.[136,245,902,928]" captionTargetBox="[340,1247,278,878]" captionTargetId="figure-58@2.[340,1247,278,878]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 2. V. oreophilum var. oreophilum: a) Flowering plant in the field b) Herbarium specimen from TUH." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5145475" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5145475/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="206">Figs. 2</figureCitation>
&amp; 
<figureCitation box="[248,261,604,630]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="2.[136,245,1691,1717]" captionText="FIGURE 3. Details of the flowers of V. oreophilum var. oreophilum." pageId="1" pageNumber="206">3</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
